Summary: Large balloon like shape - or teardrop shaped white balloon - with blinking light at bottom of object - at cloud level in sky. It first appeared to be the moon but object was not lit. It slowly passed over the Aims Community College Capus where I work.
divs: Sighting DetailsLarge balloon like shape - or teardrop shaped white balloon - with blinking light at bottom of object - at cloud level in sky. It first appeared to be the moon but object was not lit. It slowly passed over the Aims Community College Capus where I work at night as a security guard. The next day I saw event was covered in local Greeley paper - front page.
